<td valign="top">
<p>Every employer has been faced with problems regarding staff absence.  Most employees will need to take time off work due to illness at some point, however, we all know people that take ‘sickies’ or ‘duvet days’.</p>
<p>The key to dealing with absences is good management.  Set a policy, monitor it and deal promptly and fairly with any problems.</p>
<p>Moniotoring absenteeism fairly and consistently can be optimised and made simple by the use of an HR information system.  Please find more details on the "Human Resources Software" page.</p>
<p>Naturally, Eden HR Consulting can help you by advising on, setting and implementing, effective absence management policies.  We can show you how to monitor absence and we can also deal with any issues, or indeed, advise you on how to deal with such issues internally. We can also provide you with training on how to manage absence in an appropriate manner so that you have the tools you need to be able to deal with any absence as it occurs and reduce abseenteeism levels.</p>
<p> </p>
